<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Wellness Toolkit | Ginhawa</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <style>
        .breathe-circle {
            animation: breathe 8s ease-in-out infinite;
        }
        @keyframes breathe {
            0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); background-color: #93c5fd; }
            50% { transform: scale(1.5); background-color: #60a5fa; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-50 min-h-screen">
    <nav class="p-4 bg-white shadow-sm flex justify-between items-center px-8">
        <a href="/dashboard" class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-600">Ginhawa</a>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <a href="/dashboard" class="text-gray-600 hover:text-blue-600 font-medium">Back to Dashboard</a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <main class="p-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Wellness Toolkit</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-12 text-lg">Your sanctuary for mental health, study efficiency, and crisis support.</p>

        <!-- Breathing Exercise -->
        <div class="bg-white p-12 rounded-3xl shadow-sm border mb-12 text-center">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-8 text-blue-800">Box Breathing Exercise</h3>
            <div class="flex justify-center items-center h-64">
                <div class="breathe-circle w-32 h-32 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-xl">
                    <span id="breatheText">Breathe In</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <p class="mt-8 text-gray-500 italic">Inhale for 4s, Hold for 4s, Exhale for 4s, Hold for 4s.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-12">
            <!-- Coping Strategies -->
            <div class="bg-blue-50 p-8 rounded-3xl border border-blue-100">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-blue-900">Coping Strategies</h3>
                <ul class="space-y-4">
                    <li class="bg-white p-4 rounded-xl shadow-sm">
                        <strong class="block text-blue-800">Cognitive Reframing</strong>
                        <span class="text-sm text-gray-600">Instead of "I have too much to do," try "I have a lot on my plate, but I can handle one task at a time."</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="bg-white p-4 rounded-xl shadow-sm">
                        <strong class="block text-blue-800">The 5-4-3-2-1 Technique</strong>
                        <span class="text-sm text-gray-600">Ground yourself by identifying 5 things you see, 4 you feel, 3 you hear, 2 you smell, and 1 you taste.</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <!-- Study Efficiency -->
            <div class="bg-green-50 p-8 rounded-3xl border border-green-100">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-green-900">Study Efficiency Tips</h3>
                <ul class="space-y-4">
                    <li class="bg-white p-4 rounded-xl shadow-sm">
                        <strong class="block text-green-800">Active Recall</strong>
                        <span class="text-sm text-gray-600">Test yourself before you study. It primes your brain to retain the information better.</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="bg-white p-4 rounded-xl shadow-sm">
                        <strong class="block text-green-800">Time Blocking</strong>
                        <span class="text-sm text-gray-600">Dedicate specific blocks of time to one subject only. No multitasking allowed.</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Emergency / Crisis Override -->
        <div class="bg-red-600 text-white p-10 rounded-3xl shadow-xl text-center">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Feeling Overwhelmed?</h3>
            <p class="mb-8 text-red-100 text-lg">If you're feeling like you can't handle things anymore, please reach out. You are not alone.</p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
                <button onclick="alert('Connecting you with a school counselor...') " class="px-8 py-3 bg-white text-red-600 rounded-xl font-bold hover:bg-red-50 transition">Talk to a Counselor Now</button>
                <div class="w-full md:w-auto px-8 py-3 bg-red-700 text-white rounded-xl font-bold border border-red-500">Crisis Text Line: Text HOME to 741741</div>
            </div>
            <p class="mt-6 text-sm text-red-200 opacity-80 italic">* This will notify your school counselor and prioritize your support request.</p>
        </div>
    </main>

    <script>
        const texts = ["Breathe In", "Hold", "Breathe Out", "Hold"];
        let i = 0;
        setInterval(() => {
            i = (i + 1) % texts.length;
            document.getElementById('breatheText').innerText = texts[i];
        }, 2000);
    </script>
</body>
</html>
